### Purpose

Generate comprehensive project specifications that enable immediate development without ambiguity. Create 15 interconnected documents covering all aspects from user stories to deployment.

### Process

**Step 1: Create Context Document** (30 minutes)

Create `docs/_context.md`:

```markdown
